    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Change order status to 'Complete']]></title>
    <link href="http://magecode.xyz/magento/orders/change-order-status-to-complete"/>
    <updated>2015-08-09T14:22:28+00:00</updated>
    <id>http://magecode.xyz/magento/orders/change-order-status-to-complete</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>You can easily change order status programmaticaly in Magento,
but you can&rsquo;t do it freely with &ldquo;Complete&rdquo; status
because you need create invoice and shipment for this,
after these actions order status will be changed automatically to &ldquo;Complete&rdquo;.</p>

<!--more-->


<p>Here is snippet for status changing:
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
<span class='line-number'>15</span>
<span class='line-number'>16</span>
<span class='line-number'>17</span>
<span class='line-number'>18</span>
<span class='line-number'>19</span>
<span class='line-number'>20</span>
<span class='line-number'>21</span>
<span class='line-number'>22</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='php'><span class='line'><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="nx">lt</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="o">?</span><span class="nx">php</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$orderId</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="nx">ldquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="nx">your</span> <span class="nx">order</span> <span class="nx">id</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="nx">rdquo</span><span class="p">;;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">//Set state</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$order</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">Mage</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="na">getModel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="nx">lsquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="nx">sales</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="nx">order</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="nx">rsquo</span><span class="p">;)</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">load</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$orderId</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$order</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">setState</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">Mage_Sales_Model_Order</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="na">STATE_PROCESSING</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="k">true</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$order</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">save</span><span class="p">();</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">//Create invoice</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$invoice</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nv">$order</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">prepareInvoice</span><span class="p">()</span>
</span><span class='line'>                 <span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">setTransactionId</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$order</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">getId</span><span class="p">())</span>
</span><span class='line'>                 <span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">addComment</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$comment</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>                 <span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">register</span><span class="p">()</span>
</span><span class='line'>                 <span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">pay</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="nx">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nx">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="nv">$transaction_save</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">Mage</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="na">getModel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="nx">lsquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="nx">core</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="nx">resource_transaction</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="nx">rsquo</span><span class="p">;)</span>
</span><span class='line'>                 <span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">addObject</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$invoice</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>                 <span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">addObject</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$invoice</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">getOrder</span><span class="p">());</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$transaction_save</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">save</span><span class="p">();</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">//Create shipment</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$itemQty</span> <span class="o">=</span>  <span class="nv">$order</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">getItemsCollection</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">count</span><span class="p">();</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$shipment</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">Mage</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="na">getModel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="nx">lsquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="nx">sales</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="nx">service_order</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="nx">rsquo</span><span class="p">;,</span> <span class="nv">$order</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">prepareShipment</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$itemQty</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$shipment</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="k">new</span> <span class="nx">Mage_Sales_Model_Order_Shipment_Api</span><span class="p">();</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$shipmentId</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nv">$shipment</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">create</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$orderId</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<p>That&rsquo;s all.</p>
